# Hjerterum / Boly Design System

**Canonical docs:** `docs/hjerterum/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`, `docs/hjerterum/PRD.md` Â§15, `docs/hjerterum/UI_UX_GOVERNANCE.md`

## Boly App Standard (non-negotiable on `/homeowner` + `/nav`)

Production social flows are the UX baseline. Preserve:
- Professional dark UI via `globals.css` tokens
- 8px spacing grid (`--space-*`)
- DM Sans body; Fraunces only for display/hero
- Global classes: `.button`, `.button-accent`, `.card`, `.input`, `.container`
- Design-system: Toast, ConfirmDialog, PageSkeleton, EmptyState, Modal, FieldInput
- **Never** `alert()` or `confirm()`
- WCAG 2.1 AA; 44px touch targets; 16px+ inputs on mobile
- i18n via `lib/i18n/*` â€” no hard-coded user-facing strings

## Four visual planes â€” do not cross-contaminate

| Plane | CSS | Theme |
|-------|-----|-------|
| Boly App (`/homeowner`, `/nav`) | `globals.css` + phased `hjerterum-v2.css` | Dark default + light toggle |
| Finn (`/finn`) | `finn/finn.css` | Always light |
| Los (`/los`) | `los/los.css` | Always light |
| Ops (`/ops`) | `ops/ops.css` | Dark admin |

Do not import Finn/Los CSS into app routes. Lane calendar colours are shared via `--lane-*` tokens and `laneCalendarStyles.ts`.

## Tokens â€” no magic numbers

- Colours: CSS variables only (`--bg-app`, `--text-main`, `--color-accent`, `--hrt-*`, `--lane-*`)
- No inline `style={{ color: '#...' }}` for brand colours in TSX
- Spacing: `--space-*` in CSS; avoid arbitrary pixel margins in components
- Motion: `--transition-*`; honour `prefers-reduced-motion`

## Component selection order

1. `app/components/design-system/*`
2. `app/ops/components/*` (data-dense admin patterns)
3. `features/*/components/*`
4. Global CSS classes
5. New component â€” only if necessary; promote to design-system if used twice

## Required patterns

| Situation | Use |
|-----------|-----|
| Async page load | `PageSkeleton` or route `loading.tsx` |
| Empty list | `EmptyState` with next action |
| Success/error feedback | `useToast()` |
| Destructive confirm | `useConfirm()` |
| Mobile tables | `overflow-x: auto` wrapper + min-width |
| Forms | `FieldInput` or `.input` + `.label` + accessible errors |
| Skip nav | `SkipLink` on marketing/app shell |

## Tailwind

Preflight is **disabled**. Prefer global CSS classes + tokens. If using Tailwind, use `boly-*` mapped utilities â€” no arbitrary colour values.

## Before finishing UI work

- [ ] Correct visual plane
- [ ] 320px viewport â€” no unintended horizontal scroll
